dataIdInfo.idPurp: Caladapt-py is an API client that makes it easier to work with data from Cal-Adapt.org in Python and ArcGIS. The role of caladapt-py is to bring data into Python and ArcGIS and provide low-level functions to get it into the shape and format you require.
